            :op2 (p / possible-01~26
                :ARG1 (s3 / skip-01~27
                    :ARG0 y
                    :ARG1 (t2 / test~29))))
        :condition (a / apply-01~13
            :ARG0 y)
        :mode imperative~14))

# ::tok Months ago , unemployed lab technician Sandip Thapaliya excitedly called his Kathmandu sister with surprising news .
(c / call-02~9
    :ARG0 (p / person~6
        :name (n / name~6
            :op1 "Sandip"~6
            :op2 "Thapaliya"~7)
        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91~5
            :ARG2 (t / technician~5
                :mod (l / lab~4)))
        :ARG1-of (e / employ-01~3
            :polarity -~2))
    :ARG1 (p2 / person~10
        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-rel-role-91~12
            :ARG1 p
            :ARG2 (s / sister~12))
        :location (c2 / city~11
            :name (n2 / name~11
                :op1 "Kathmandu"~11)))
    :ARG1 (n3 / news~15
        :ARG0-of (s2 / surprise-01~14))
    :manner (e2 / excite-01~8
        :ARG1 p)
    :time (b / before~13
        :quant (m2 / multiple~0
            :op1 (t2 / temporal-quantity~0
                :quant 1~1
                :unit (m / month~0)))
        :op1 (n4 / now~16)))
